scenes.description: Vestia Zeta presents the 'Fancy a dance with me...? Diorama Acrylic Stand' merchandise.
Vestia Zeta showcases the 'Cozy BaZeta Hoodie'.
Vestia Zeta introduces the 'Pocket size BaZeta Plushie Keychain'.
Vestia Zeta presents the final item, 'Zecretary's Pin Me Down Pin Badge'.
